Build dependencies:
- C++11 capable compiler
- Curses
- DejaVu Sans Mono
- freeglut and glew
- FreeType2
- Jam
- LLVM and Clang > 3.7
- OpenGLES >= 2.0

Compile:
$ jam

Run the tests with any TAP harness:
$ prove
